### ----------------------------------------
### SUPER ADMIN DASHBOARD
### ----------------------------------------

### Get dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get appointments overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/appointments?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-14
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get patients overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get encounters overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/encounters?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-14
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get staff availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/staff-availability?hospitalId={{hospitalId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get patient consents overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/dashboard/patient-consents
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### SUPER ADMIN — ORGANIZATIONS
### ----------------------------------------

### List all organizations (super admin view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/organizations?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get organization details
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/organizations/{{organizationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Suspend organization
PUT {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/organizations/{{organizationId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Non-compliance with security policies"
}

### Reactivate organization
PUT {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/organizations/{{organizationId}}/reactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### SUPER ADMIN — USER GOVERNANCE
### ----------------------------------------

### List all users (governance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Search users
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users/search?query=john&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Lock user account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users/{{userId}}/lock
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Suspicious login activity detected"
}

### Unlock user account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users/{{userId}}/unlock
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Force password reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users/{{userId}}/force-password-reset
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get user activity log
GET {{baseUrl}}/super-admin/users/{{userId}}/activity?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

